The X13.Home project, http://X13Home.org, http://x13home.github.io

X13.devices
===========

Firmware section for project X13.Home
Version 3.1.0

Automation System oriented to "Smart House" over MQTT(SN) protocol

Devices
  Board: Arduino Nano/Uno, uC: ATMega328P, Fosc = 16M
    A1Sn10      PHY1 - Serial Port
    A1SC10      PHY1 - Serial Port, PHY2 - CC1101

  Board: Arduino Mega, uC: ATMega2560
    A4Sn10      PHY1 - Serial Port

  Board: uNode v2.0, uC: ATMega328P, pinout not compatible with Firmware 2.6/3.0
    A1Cn12      PHY1 - CC1101, old name RFNDUP
    A1En12      PHY1 - ENC28J60, old name LNNDEN
    A1Rn11      PHY1 - RFM12(MRF49XA), old name RFNDUN
    A1SC12      PHY1 - UART, PHY2 - CC1101, old name RFGWUP
    A1Sn12      PHY1 - UART, old name DMGWDM
    A1SR11      PHY1 - UART, PHY2 - RFM12(MRF49XA), old name RFGWUN
    
  Board: GS, uC: ST32F051K8 - ARM Cortex M0
    S2SC14      PHY1 - UART, PHY2 - CC1101

  Board: S2EC13, uC: ST32F051C8 - ARM Cortex M0
    S2Cn13      PHY1 - CC1101
    S2EC13      PHY1 - ENC28J60, PHY2 - CC1101
    S2En13      PHY1 - ENC28J60
    S2Sn13      PHY1 - UART

  Board: Discovery F0, uC: STM32F051R8 - ARM Cortex M0
    S2Sn10      PHY1 - UART

  Board: Nucleo, uC: STM32F091RC - ARM Cortex M0
    S2Sn11      PHY1 - UART

  Board: / Board: Maple Mini, uC: STM32F103CB - ARM Cortex M3
    S3Cn10      PHY1 - CC1101
    S3En10      PHY1 - ENC28J60
    S3SC10      PHY1 - UART, PHY2 - CC1101
    S3Sn10      PHY1 - UART
